Class HttpInputStreamWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.io.InputStream
      • com.emc.esu.api.HttpInputStreamWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Closeable, java.lang.AutoCloseable

    public class HttpInputStreamWrapper
extends java.io.InputStream
    Wraps the HTTP input stream and connection object so that when the stream is closed the connection can be closed as well.
